00:41:24.280 --> 00:41:25.070
in the visual spectrum.

00:41:25.070 --> 00:41:27.370
It doesn't go outside of the
visual spectrum, but it remaps

00:41:27.370 --> 00:41:30.770
them so that they match more the
colorblind person's eyes.

00:41:30.770 --> 00:41:33.215
So the colorblind people can
look through this and they can

00:41:33.215 --> 00:41:35.530
now tell the difference between
the red and the green

00:41:35.530 --> 00:41:36.990
in the way they can't tell
with their own eyes.

00:41:36.990 --> 00:41:38.920
They can just hold up
their phone and say,

00:41:38.920 --> 00:41:40.750
oh, now I see that.

00:41:40.750 --> 00:41:42.320
That's kind of cool.

00:41:42.320 --> 00:41:44.610
Any more questions?

